00:05:28.910 --> 00:05:31.060
We found that collaborative
coding on Unity

00:05:31.060 --> 00:05:31.970
was really hard.

00:05:31.970 --> 00:05:34.180
Certain changes
to the main scene

00:05:34.180 --> 00:05:37.890
