00:06:46.230 --> 00:06:48.640
Working early and
quickly-- this was partly

00:06:48.640 --> 00:06:52.250
hindered because we lost
at least four days of work

00:06:52.250 --> 00:06:54.320
because we were trying
to get Flixel set up.

00:06:54.320 --> 00:06:55.631
