00:06:55.631 --> 00:06:57.006
And we had to
switch to Unity, so

00:06:57.006 --> 00:06:59.010
basically starting
over from scratch.

00:06:59.010 --> 00:07:01.800
Working early and quickly
is super important

00:07:01.800 --> 00:07:04.000
because we ended
up having to drop

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:07.280
quite a few features because we
didn't get enough done on time.

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:11.639
