took a long time.

00:07:22.050 --> 00:07:23.440
It ended up looking
really, really nice,

00:07:23.440 --> 00:07:24.731
as you can see in the pictures.

00:07:24.731 --> 00:07:27.600
But the time investment
was a huge investment

00:07:27.600 --> 00:07:30.560
that we could have used to put
in some more complex mechanic

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:32.670
into our game.

00:07:32.670 --> 00:07:35.810
And future improvements, team
communication and availability

00:07:35.810 --> 00:07:37.340
is a huge one.

00:07:37.340 --> 00:07:40.002
We, as Rachel said, we
had a task assignment

00:07:40.002 --> 00:07:40.710
at the beginning.

00:07:40.710 --> 00:07:42.210
But then due to
people's schedule,

00:07:42.210 --> 00:07:43.835
