initial task list.

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:47.777
So people ended up having to
pick up other people's tasks.

00:07:47.777 --> 00:07:49.318
And it became very
hard to figure out

00:07:49.318 --> 00:07:50.350
who was working on what.

00:07:50.350 --> 00:07:54.440
And scheduling meetings
was near impossible.

00:07:54.440 --> 00:07:57.660
Getting familiar with the game
engine-- using Unity at first

00:07:57.660 --> 00:08:00.150
was very hard because we
weren't sure how scenes work.

00:08:00.150 --> 00:08:02.080
