about the code,

00:08:06.120 --> 00:08:08.746
and not have to worry about
all the user interface stuff

00:08:08.746 --> 00:08:10.810
that Unity does.

00:08:10.810 --> 00:08:13.420
And that would have made our
game develop a lot quicker.

00:08:13.420 --> 00:08:15.370
And setting deadlines
was very important.

00:08:15.370 --> 00:08:16.740
