task to be assigned,

00:08:20.820 --> 00:08:22.700
or when we wanted each
task to be finished.

00:08:22.700 --> 00:08:25.240
And that would have
helped push along our game

00:08:25.240 --> 00:08:27.924
and get some of them more
mechanics that we wanted in it.

