00:16:01.720 --> 00:16:04.160
But from an outside
perspective, a scrum master

00:16:04.160 --> 00:16:08.160
might be able to more accurately
help with estimates and stuff

00:16:08.160 --> 00:16:08.890
like that.

00:16:08.890 --> 00:16:11.110
So a dedicated
